{"id":"23033","name":"忍法帖•缭乱破魔","rarity":5,"path":"Mage","desc":"「忍界」某地，灰惨的阴霾笼罩着城市。\n「咿呀——！」\n少女的身影在怪物之中穿行，其残影如同绚丽的色彩挥洒于没有月光的大地。\n烟尘之中，「邪忍」们痛苦呻吟，惊疑不定。\n「你…是谁……」\n「在下忍号『乱破』，一心不乱，破邪显正是也。」\n「邪忍」们面面相觑，意欲四处逃窜。\n「阁下，准备好念诵辞世句了吗——」\n手里剑如流光旋转，危险的气息席卷而来。\n「奥义•缭乱灭破杀阵！」\n身后的爆炸照亮了满目疮痍的夜晚。\n她深吸一口气，跃入如重金属般喧嚣的霓虹灯光之中。\n「此等邪祟，实际丑恶。缭乱忍侠的壮绝•狩猎，仍需继续……」","icon":"icon/light_cone/23033.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/23033.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/23033.png","ranks":{"id":"23033","skill":"除邪","desc":"使装备者的击破特攻提高#1[i]%。进入战斗时立即恢复#2[f1]点能量，且装备者施放终结技后获得【雷遁】，施放2次普攻后，装备者行动提前#3[i]%，并移除【雷遁】。装备者施放终结技后会重置【雷遁】。","params":[[0.6,30,0.5],[0.7,32.5,0.55],[0.8,35,0.6],[0.9,37.5,0.65],[1,40,0.7]],"properties":[[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.6}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.7}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.8}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.9}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":1}]]},"promotions":{"id":"23033","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":26.4,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":24,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":58.08,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":100.32,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":142.56,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":184.8,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":168,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":227.04,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":269.28,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"114001","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110201","num":4},{"id":"114001","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110202","num":4},{"id":"114002","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110202","num":8},{"id":"114002","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000},{"